    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Specialized form of table at which one ate oysters; circular in form with a hole in the center, under which stood a basket for the empty shells.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
